branchCategory.name: CJ
branchCategory.description: <p>Miniature cylinders series 90-CDJ2 is available in double acting offer stainless steel tubing, stainless steel rods and materials that are compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. The series is available in bore sizes 10, 16mm and stroke lengths from 15mm to 200mm. Mounting options include basic, foot, front flange, and double rear clevis. Series 90-CDJ2 is auto switch capable.</p>

branchItem.name: 90-C(D)J2, Air Cylinder, Double Acting, Single Rod
branchItem.description: <p>Air cylinder series 90-C(D)J2 miniature cylinders available in double acting and offer stainless steel tubing and stainless steel rods. 90-CJ2 is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. 91-CJ2 includes a "Lub-retainer" and is compatible with low dew point (40°C) applications. The series is available in bore sizes 10mm and 16mm and stroke lengths up to 200mm. </p>
